      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WADE'S EDGE (2) chased the lead early from the inside and boxed on well to finish third, beaten 6 lengths (23.33) at this track in a Grade 5 over 400m. Expected to feature in the finish again. PITMAN RINGO (1) turned in a plain run last time when fifth at this track over 515m behind Hello Peck (30.59) in a Grade 5. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from eight starts. Worth following up. IMPERATOR (4) turned in a plain performance last time when fifth at this track over 400m behind Zipper Surprise (23.35) in a Grade 5. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Should be in this for a long way. HOT WORK (5) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to bounce back.",
